1. Hardware Traceability

“The most important short-term topic is clearly the hardware traceability journey that we are integrating directly into Le Comptoir.

We are almost done with the development of the hardware return declaration process.

Just as a reminder, this process will ensure full traceability for all hardware return scenarios.

The technician will scan the equipment, the application will retrieve the asset information directly from the CMDB, and the whole process will end with a user signature and proof storage.

During the pilot phase, I will organize a dedicated demonstration session to show exactly how the process works and how the teams will use it operationally.

There are too many details to explain today, so we will really focus on this topic separately.”

