4. Badge Database Integration

“Another important topic concerns the welcome tablet in France.

Le Comptoir will soon be connected directly to the badge management database — currently managed by IMEX.

This means that for new joiners or temporary badge loans, the application will immediately identify the user behind the badge in real time.

And if some of your countries or territories have the possibility to expose an API from their own badge management provider, we can also study similar integrations locally.”

⸻

5. AI Analytics & Insights

“Moving now to more mid-term initiatives.

We are planning to introduce AI capabilities into the Power BI analytics.

The objective is to automatically analyze dissatisfaction reasons, user comments, and treatment times by category.

The AI will analyze user sentiment, categorize dissatisfaction drivers, and provide rankings and insights for each counter.

The idea is really to help pre-analyze the data and simplify the identification of improvement opportunities.”

